resources.description: This data set has been sourced from 'Evaluation Study on Rashtriya Sam Vikas Yojna (RSVY), 2010' by PEO, Planning commission. The outcome is based on the sample survey undertaken by Programme Evaluation Organisation (PEO), Planning commission which covered 11 states, 15 districts and a total of 28 blocks of India for 'Evaluation Study on Rashtriya Sam Vikas Yojna (RSVY), 2010'.
